Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女作为超世脱俗的天才儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被寄养在设施中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间是在一岁之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女开始会说话之后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在那里得知了游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}称之为智能检查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她被人要求玩了许多游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是太过无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论跟谁玩都感觉不到快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后 在过了两年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女和似乎是母亲的女性再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比自己年长七岁的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在大人们的对话中 适当地附和着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}展露出空虚且无感情的笑容 面对这样的他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女张开了长时间闭住的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是个空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐 我们来玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(960,1005)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}『　　』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(922.5,1005)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对『　　』来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\blur3\pos(922.5,1005)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对『　　』来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是做了恶梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就去端暖和的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人 您在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小多拉惊惶失措地说您突然飞奔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在想您是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在的 您有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉普莉尔的主人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么现在要特地问这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么和吉普莉尔战斗的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要求史蒂芙迷上我的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}揭露了东部联合的游戏内容的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是白大人与小多拉祖父的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钦佩白大人那举世无双的才智和智谋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以跟随了您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟随了白？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(1005,1005)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作为艾尔奇亚的王 人类种的全权代理人——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 除了白以外还存在其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是没有根据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}城内当然不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\fs54}门牌：白的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管将询问范围扩大到城镇周边的所有地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在抗议游行之中也没有人知道那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人在我们不知道的一段时间内和什么人进行了游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失败后被人篡改了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会 这种事到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东部联合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是他们的话 应该是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们来游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赌上灌输给主人的虚伪的存在进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虚伪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后 虽然十分失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能请您输给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 游戏就决定是国际象棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虚伪的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那真的是 虚伪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才会渐渐消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐 白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然有人说人是会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但真的是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部 全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都在渐渐消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果许愿说想要飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能长出翅膀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为是不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该改变的不是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是手段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有去创造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}创造出现在的自己能够飞上天的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让白飞上天的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慢慢地思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部都是虚伪…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都是谎言…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}消失了的话就会轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(945,1005)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}『　　』？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(960,1005)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}『　　』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(915,1005)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对『　　』来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\blur3\pos(922.5,1005)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对『　　』来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有失败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要取胜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥——空是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝对 绝对是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(960,999,960,1065,520,920)\blur3}存在 是存在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请冷静下来 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请合乎逻辑地考虑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的确认为不存在才是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那个人一定存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小多拉 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为 不可能输的嘛
Comment: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}••
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}史蒂芙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 不可能输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定有什么缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}创造出这个状况的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你太任凭感情行事了 再多…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忙于处理游行活动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那之后和白在王座上玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是前天 十九日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改变提问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前天的晚上你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是那天晚上的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 那个 诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有了 这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后只剩下确认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在摸史蒂芙的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 我该怎么反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明我对你说过迷上我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是「除了主人之外 有要求小多拉迷上他的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错　因为这么要求的是哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 空的存在不是已经确信了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我到底是为了什么而被揉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是谢礼 因为要是没有史蒂芙我就察觉不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么试着想想看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}存在空这个人并且消失的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大约一天半 从我们所有人脑中消失的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然使用大规模的魔法并不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那样的话一定会留下痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是游戏的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是有向盟约宣誓后进行的游戏中有这样的设定呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是作为全权代理人进行的游戏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(1177.5,1005)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其影响会波及所有人类种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是对吉普莉尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 在侍奉主人的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我换而言之就是附属物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该可以考虑成受到其影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 这到底是什么游戏呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我相信着白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白 我们两人无论何时都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥不会让白一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白… 你在吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白 你还在吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:09:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白 你在哪里 你能握紧我还有知觉的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了让我不疯掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算烧坏也可以 思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个状况——哥所托付给我的这个状况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使用一切剩下的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们两人是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话 哥就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总是在游戏开始之前就获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因约定而结合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不是少年漫画的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 再多思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再多多思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去拿下最后一块拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为此进行的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与东部联合的战斗所需的手牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}道具 智慧 监视者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(930,1005)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}森精种？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(1072.5,1005)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到森精种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要怎么得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向爱尔文•加尔得挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米并不相信哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能会答应这种要求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相互争夺存在的游戏 的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相互争夺存在的游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs42\pos(1545,807)\fad(800,300)}<Sky•Walk>{\fs60}\N分离法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}构成自己存在的三十二个棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反映出心理深层次的优先级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}按照重要的顺序 从一开始分配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 哪个棋子构成着自己的什么部分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在被对方取得之后 确确实实失去后才会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(1057.5,1005)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如说 你旁边森精种的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手臂和脚 神经和记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后就连存在本身都会被剥夺 完全认知不出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盟约其五 被挑战的一方拥有游戏内容的决定权
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不愿意的话 游戏不会成立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(1170,1005)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}菲 这个男人在宣言赌上人类种的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能放着他不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明我还有些期待着是不是能够和解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我接受和解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(1147.5,1005)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你能相信我把那个森精种让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎么可能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你赌上的东西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赢的一方能要求对方两件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如说 将游戏结果永久确立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将对方的存在永远葬送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}篡改彼此伙伴的一个记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使她成为同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 争夺双方的存在和同伴生死的权利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你简直是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 因为疯了顺便提案一条重要的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉普莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能做出相互争夺存在的游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是实体化首尾接龙那样的虚拟世界的话 是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(883.5,1005)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果和森精种一起合作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}合作？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和那些森林里的乡下人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在远古大战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被我的一发天击连国都被轰飞的像垃圾一样的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能做到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那群乡下人对编织复杂的术式多少还是很擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那空就是进行了那个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后消除了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然如此的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那果然是已经输了然后存在被消除了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果胜利了的话空应该是存在的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果既不是赢了也不是输了的话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}游戏还在进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉普莉尔 魔法的反应 这间房间里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白是在这里醒来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥和白的寝室 明明在别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是却在这个房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥说过不会让我一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确实有魔法在展开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过精确的位置就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事到如此只有把所及之处都找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小多拉 竟然在什么都没有的地方摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为已经不需要再增加角色设定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}摔倒了？ 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黑白棋的棋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(855,1005)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是森精种文字的三呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么只有棋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为还没有被使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算无法被认知但还是在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 就算是知道了也只有三枚棋子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连我们这边是执白还是执黑都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那种事很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥说过 我们两个人合起来才算一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个游戏白也参加在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我提案一个非常重要的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}双方的伙伴也参加游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当玩家无法继续的情况下可以代打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以记忆保留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看得到吗？ 棋盘？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看不见 但我知道哥的话会怎么走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这是故意输给我的下法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 这样就是能赢的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎样诱导对方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么？你的记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道你想让我就这样抢夺你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后证明背后没有任何种族的事实吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不算坏的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎样传达自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就无法继续游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是游戏还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么回事？ 为什么游戏还不结束？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那三枚棋子到底是空的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎样欺骗对方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后 怎样取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥 很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话没人能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了哥和白以外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的棋子里所含有的构成哥的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第三 取得游戏胜利的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二 对白的绝对信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后第一 白个人的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 你可以揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白 应该更早一点 更早一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然忘记了主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米 振作一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 我要按照预定提出要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以任你摆布 但是克拉米…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 要求一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将双方所争夺的记忆 固定与归还
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保留从对方那里得到的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同时把被夺取的记忆还给了本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米和主人就成为了知晓对方一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}值得信赖的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这正是主人所追求的最后一片拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs48\pos(1050,1005)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要求二 那边的森精种——菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要获得篡改你记忆的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系的 菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个男人的要求只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是要我们当间谍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不愧是偷窥过我脑中记忆的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}间谍？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过后告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看过你脑中的记忆后 我改变了想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我赞同你的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥 很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可以夸我是可以引以为傲的哥哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是白引以为傲的哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被你这么老实地称赞 哥会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白 差不多可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准备好了 随时可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是超可怕啊 真再也不会做这种事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也是主人真正的姿态…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…也说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an7\fs54}注：出自圣龙战记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比Salamander还要快得多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(925.5,522)}请稍后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为大人真是悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs42\pos(1596,811.5)}<Blue・Rose>{\fs60}\N指向法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}誰にも言えない孤独を抱えたまま一人で泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}誰にも上手に笑えない僕ら二人出会って笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}真夜中すぎに　想像の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}どうしようもない気持ちをただ押しやって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}サヨナラ　僕らはきっと生まれ変われるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}悲しみに手を振るんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そしていつか空っぽのままの心に灯りをともすように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}とぎれとぎれの　言葉を探して繋ぎ止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}それでもたった二人の世界は続いてくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}空に祈るように　どうか永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}将无法对别人说出口的孤独藏于心中 一个人哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无法对别人好好笑出来的我们 相遇了欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}在午夜过后之时 在想象深处之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}只是将无可奈何的心情抛在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}再见了 因为我们一定能够重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}对悲伤挥挥手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}然后曾经空荡荡的心灵就会像点燃了明灯一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}寻找断断续续的话语 将它们系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}尽管如此两人的世界还是会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}像天空祈祷 请一定要相伴永远
